item.title: CVE-2022-46768|2024-09-17T03:37:51.502Z -- zabbix -- web%20service%20report%20generation
item.description: Arbitrary file read vulnerability exists in Zabbix Web Service Report Generation, which listens on the port 10053. The service does not have proper validation for URL parameters before reading the files.
